Text.Value: • Measures and displays .001 to 350 cGy/hr Gamma radiation dose rate
• The Radiacmeter can measure, store, and display an accumulated Dose from .001 to 999 cGy/hr
• Alarm capability for Dose and Dose Rate
• Accuracy is rated at plus or minus 20% of True Dose and Dose Rate
• Possesses a 'Sleep Mode' with an automatic wake-up capability
• The Radiacmeter will 'turn on' to the Normal Operation Mode if radiation is present and exceeds the Alarm Mode level
